description:
McpcPCellProfile: Table storing configuration profiles for cells in a 5G/4G network, including cell identification, location, and user configuration group type.

dateTime: Timestamp indicating when the profile data was recorded.
Area_Name: Name of the geographical area where the cell is located.
CellId: Unique identifier for the cell.
Id2: Redundant/alternative cell identifier.
Id3:  Ancillary identifier (likely internal or specific to the data source).
Id4:  Ancillary identifier (likely default profile indicator).
vsDataType:  Data type identifier specifying the table type.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format used (Ericsson specific).
McpcPCellProfile.userLabel: User-defined label for the profile (currently empty).
McpcPCellProfile.reservedBy:  Indicates if the profile is reserved (currently empty).
McpcPCellProfile.ueConfGroupType: Type of UE configuration group associated with the profile.
McpcPCellProfile.mcpcPCellProfileId: Unique identifier for the specific cell profile.
